As you can see I am not uber, but I have lots of room to grow in my post-50's. Throw in GEB's, a nice 10int robe or something, and blue diamond stuff I will have around 190-195int with decent resists. It isn't a rule to have 200int. Its recommended but I haven't heard of a case where a wizard was a failure because he only made it to 190.<br>
